/**
 * MappingService - Complete mapping system with ALL 24,619 console→dashboard cell mappings
 * 
 * Structure:
 * - F_PL_YTD: P&L data mappings
 * - F_BS: Balance Sheet data mappings
 * - F_CF_YTD: Cash Flow data mappings
 * 
 * Each mapping: {sheet, consoleCol, consoleRow, entity, month, dashboardRow, dashboardCol}
 * 
 * Usage:
 *   getMapping(entity, month, consoleRow, consoleCol) → {dashboardRow, dashboardCol}
 *   getMonthlyMappings(month) → all mappings for that month
 */
